snippet.title: Bleed 2 Teaser 1: Launching Feb 8!
snippet.description:
Bleed 2 is out Feb 8! I'm releasing small teasers each week until then. They're mostly for social media, but why not put them here too?
Steam Page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/396350
Humble Page: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/bleed-2
